1. helm search repo jenkins

2. helm repo update

3. helm install jenkins stable/jenkins 

4. helm list

5. kubectl get all

6. helm uninstall jenkins

7. helm list

8. helm repo add stable https://kubernetes-charts.storage.googleapis.com

9. helm repo update

10. helm delete ---> helm uninstall

11. helm inspect ---> helm show

12. helm fetch  ---> helm pull

13. --purge is now default (to override: helm uninstall --keep-history) by default uninstall command delete history

14. helm init ---> is now removed

15. helm 2to3 convert --dry-run croc-hunter

16. --generate-name ---> Old Style Helm2 ---> auto-generated unless overridden ---> New Style helm3 ---> error unless auto-generation requested

